esigning" target="_blank">Re-sign Oxygen Builder shortcodes</a>. (opens a new window)<br />» <a class="ai1wm-no-underline" href="https://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/all-in-one-wp-migration?rate=5#postform" target="_blank">Optionally, review the plugin</a>. (opens a new window)'=>'» <a class="ai1wm-no-underline" href="%s" target="_blank">儲存永久連結結構</a>。(在新視窗中開啟)<br />» <a class="ai1wm-no-underline" href="https://oxygenbuilder.com/documentation/other/importing-exporting/#resigning" target="_blank">重新簽署 Oxygen Builder 短代碼</a>。(在新視窗中開啟)<br />» <a class="ai1wm-no-underline" href="https://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/all-in-one-wp-migration?rate=5#postform" target="_blank">為外掛評分 (選填)</a>。(在新視窗中開啟)','Archiving %d media files...<br />%d%% complete'=>'正在壓縮 %d 個媒體檔案...<br />已完成 %d%%','Archiving %d content files...<br />%d%% complete'=>'正在壓縮 %d 個內容檔案...<br />已完成 %d%%','Done retrieving a list of WordPress content files.'=>'擷取 WordPress 內容檔案清單已完成。','Retrieving a list of WordPress content files...'=>'正在擷取 WordPress 內容檔案清單...','Done retrieving a list of WordPress media files.'=>'擷取 WordPress 媒體檔案清單已完成。','Retrieving a list of WordPress media files...'=>'正在擷取 WordPress 媒體檔案清單...','There is not enough space available on the disk.<br />Free up %s of disk space.'=>'磁碟沒有足夠的空間。<br />釋放 %s 所佔用的磁碟空間。','I have enough disk space'=>'這台主機有足夠的磁碟空間','Done preparing options.'=>'選項準備已完成。','%s is not the latest version. You must update the plugin before you can use it. '=>'%s 不是最新版本。在使用它之前，必須先更新外掛。','Your backup is from a PHP %s but the site that you are importing to is PHP %s. This could cause the import to fail. Technical details: https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/migrate-wordpress-from-php-5-to-php-7/'=>'這份備份檔案來自執行環境為 PHP %s 的網站，卻要匯入至執行環境為 PHP %s 的主機，這種狀況可能會導致無法匯入。技術詳細資料: https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/migrate-wordpress-from-php-5-to-php-7/','Refreshing backup list...'=>'重新整理備份檔案清單...','<h3>Site could not be imported</h3><p>Please make sure that storage directory <strong>%s</strong> has read and write permissions.</p><p><a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-file-permissions/" target="_blank">Technical details</a></p>'=>'<h3>無法匯入網站</h3><p>請確認系統具備對儲存目錄 <strong>%s</strong> 的讀取及寫入權限。</p><p><a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-file-permissions/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a></p>','<h3>Site could not be exported</h3><p>Please make sure that storage directory <strong>%s</strong> has read and write permissions.</p><p><a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-file-permissions/" target="_blank">Technical details</a></p>'=>'<h3>無法匯出網站</h3><p>請確認系統具備對儲存目錄 <strong>%s</strong> 的讀取及寫入權限。</p><p><a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-file-permissions/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a></p>','<h3>Site could not be restored</h3><p>Please make sure that storage directory <strong>%s</strong> has read and write permissions.</p><p><a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-file-permissions/" target="_blank">Technical details</a></p>'=>'<h3>無法還原網站</h3><p>請確認系統具備對儲存目錄 <strong>%s</strong> 的讀取及寫入權限。</p><p><a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-file-permissions/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a></p>','All-in-One WP Migration: Your current profile role does not have Export/Import capabilities enabled. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/how-to-add-import-and-export-capabilities-to-wordpress-users/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'All-in-One WP Migration: 目前的登入身分沒有進行匯出/匯入的權限<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/how-to-add-import-and-export-capabilities-to-wordpress-users/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a>','To choose a file please go inside the link and click on the browse button.'=>'如需選取檔案，請點擊連結並點擊 [瀏覽] 按鈕。','» <a class="ai1wm-no-underline" href="%s" target="_blank">Save permalinks structure</a>. (opens a new window)<br />» <a class="ai1wm-no-underline" href="https://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/all-in-one-wp-migration?rate=5#postform" target="_blank">Optionally, review the plugin</a>. (opens a new window)'=>'» <a class="ai1wm-no-underline" href="%s" target="_blank">儲存永久連結結構</a>。(在新視窗中開啟)<br />» <a class="ai1wm-no-underline" href="https://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/all-in-one-wp-migration?rate=5#postform" target="_blank">為外掛評分 (選填)</a>。(在新視窗中開啟)','"Restore" functionality is available in a <a href="https://servmask.com/products/unlimited-extension" target="_blank">paid extension</a>.<br />You could also download the backup and then use "Import from file".'=>'從網站主機伺服器直接還原為<a href="https://servmask.com/products/unlimited-extension" target="_blank">付費擴充功能</a>。<br />網站管理員可以改為先下載備份檔案，然後再從備份檔案匯入網站。','Finish'=>'完成','Click to set a label for this backup'=>'點擊以設定這個備份檔案的標籤','<a href="%s" class="ai1wm-button-green ai1wm-emphasize ai1wm-button-download" title="%s" download="%s"><span>Download %s</span><em>Size: %s</em></a>'=>'<a href="%s" class="ai1wm-button-green ai1wm-emphasize ai1wm-button-download" title="%s" download="%s"><span>下載 %s 的匯出檔</span>∣<strong>檔案大小: %s</strong></a>','Unable to export: %s'=>'無法匯出: %s','Unable to import: %s'=>'無法匯入: %s','Unable to import. Error code: %s. %s'=>'無法匯入。錯誤代碼: %s。%s','The import process will overwrite your website including the database, media, plugins, and themes. Are you sure to proceed?'=>'匯入程序會覆寫這個網站，包含資料庫、媒體檔案、外掛及佈景主題。確定要繼續執行？','Please make sure that your file was exported using <strong>All-in-One WP Migration</strong> plugin. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-backup-file/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'請確定目前的檔案是由 <strong>All-in-One WP Migration</strong> 外掛匯出。<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-backup-file/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a>','The archive file is corrupted. Follow <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/corrupted-archive/" target="_blank">this article</a> to resolve the problem.'=>'壓縮檔已損毀。請參考<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/corrupted-archive/" target="_blank">這篇文章</a>以解決問題。','Your PHP is 32-bit. In order to import your file, please change your PHP version to 64-bit and try again. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/php-32bit/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'這個網站的 PHP 執行環境為 32 位元版本，請改用 64 位元版本後再試一次。<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/php-32bit/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a>','<i class="ai1wm-import-info">Your backup is from a PHP %s but the site that you are importing to is PHP %s. This could cause the import to fail. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/migrate-wordpress-from-php-5-to-php-7/" target="_blank">Technical details</a></i>'=>'<i class="ai1wm-import-info">這份備份檔案來自執行環境為 PHP %s 的網站，卻要匯入至執行環境為 PHP %s 的主機，這種狀況可能會導致無法匯入。<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/migrate-wordpress-from-php-5-to-php-7/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a></i>','The import process will overwrite your website including the database, media, plugins, and themes. Please ensure that you have a backup of your data before proceeding to the next step.'=>'匯入程序會覆寫這個網站，包含資料庫、媒體檔案、外掛及佈景主題。在繼續匯入網站前，請確認已為這個網站進行備份。','<strong>%s</strong> is not the latest version. You must <a href="%s">update the plugin</a> before you can use it. <br />'=>'<strong>%s</strong> 不是最新版本。在使用它之前，必須先<a href="%s">更新外掛</a>。<br />','The file that you are trying to import is over the maximum upload file size limit of <strong>%s</strong>.<br />You can remove this restriction by purchasing our <a href="https://servmask.com/products/unlimited-extension" target="_blank">Unlimited Extension</a>.'=>'目前匯入的檔案超過 <strong>%s</strong> 的上傳檔案大小上限。<br />如需解除這項限制，請購買<a href="https://servmask.com/products/unlimited-extension" target="_blank">Unlimited 擴充功能</a>。','The file type that you have tried to upload is not compatible with this plugin. Please ensure that your file is a <strong>.wpress</strong> file that was created with the All-in-One WP migration plugin. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-backup-file/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'目前上傳的檔案類型與這個外掛不相容。請確認要上傳的檔案是由 All-in-One WP Migration 建立的 <strong>.wpress</strong> 檔案。<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-backup-file/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a>','WordPress Multisite is supported via our All-in-One WP Migration Multisite Extension. You can get a copy of it here'=>'All-in-One WP Migration 的 Multisite 擴充功能支援 WordPress 多站網路。請前往授權頁面付費購買。','All-in-One WP Migration is not able to create <strong>%s</strong> file. Try to change permissions of the parent folder or send us an email at <a href="mailto:support@servmask.com">support@servmask.com</a> for assistance.'=>'All-in-One WP Migration 無法建立 <strong>%s</strong> 檔案。請變更上層資料夾權限，或傳送電子郵件<a href="mailto:support@servmask.com">聯絡我們</a>取得協助。','All-in-One WP Migration is not able to create <strong>%s</strong> folder. You will need to create this folder and grant it read/write/execute permissions (0777) for the All-in-One WP Migration plugin to function properly.'=>'All-in-One WP Migration 無法建立 <strong>%s</strong> 資料夾。網站管理員必須為 All-in-One WP Migration 建立對應資料夾，並設定為 0777 (讀取/寫入/執行) 權限，外掛才能正確執行。','or'=>'或','How-to: Increase maximum upload file size'=>'如何提高上傳檔案大小上限','Maximum upload file size: <strong>%s</strong>.'=>'上傳檔案大小上限: <strong>%s</strong>。','The file is too large for this server.'=>'上傳的檔案大小超過這台伺服器的上限。','<a href="https://help.servmask.com/2018/10/27/how-to-increase-maximum-upload-file-size-in-wordpress/" target="_blank">How-to: Increase maximum upload file size</a> or '=>'<a href="https://help.servmask.com/2018/10/27/how-to-increase-maximum-upload-file-size-in-wordpress/" target="_blank">如何提高上傳檔案大小上限</a>或','Your file exceeds the maximum upload size for this site: <strong>%s</strong><br />%s%s'=>'檔案已超過這個網站的檔案上傳大小限制: <strong>%s</strong><br />%s%s','Drag & Drop a backup to import it'=>'拖放備份檔案以匯入','Exporting database...<br />%d%% complete<br />%s records saved'=>'正在匯出資料庫...<br />已完成 %d%%<br />%s 筆資料已儲存','Restoring a backup is available via Unlimited extension. <a href="https://servmask.com/products/unlimited-extension" target="_blank">Get it here</a>'=>'從網站主機伺服器直接還原為付費版 Unlimited 擴充功能。<a href="https://servmask.com/products/unlimited-extension" target="_blank">立即購買</a>','All-in-One WP Migration Command'=>'All-in-One WP Migration 命令','Preparing to export...'=>'正在準備匯出網站...','%s ago'=>'%s前','Your purchase ID is invalid, please <a href="mailto:support@servmask.com">contact us</a>'=>'無效的購買 ID。請<a href="mailto:support@servmask.com">聯絡我們</a>','Are you sure you want to delete this file?'=>'確定要刪除這個備份檔案？','Please do not close this browser window or your import will fail'=>'請不要關閉這個瀏覽器視窗，否則匯入程序會失敗。','Continue'=>'繼續','Proceed'=>'繼續','Stop import'=>'停止匯入程序','Please wait, stopping the import...'=>'請稍候，正在停止匯入程序...','Unable to stop the import. Refresh the page and try again'=>'無法停止匯入程序，請重新整理頁面後再試一次。','Unable to prepare blogs on import. Refresh the page and try again'=>'無法進行匯入程序準備工作，請重新整理頁面後再試一次。','Unable to confirm the import. Refresh the page and try again'=>'無法確認匯入程序，請重新整理頁面後再試一次。','Unable to start the import. Refresh the page and try again'=>'無法啟動匯入程序，請重新整理頁面後再試一次。','You are about to stop importing your website, are you sure?'=>'即將停止匯入網站，確定要繼續操作嗎？','Thanks for submitting your request!'=>'感謝提交你的要求！','Thanks for submitting your feedback!'=>'感謝提交你的意見反應！','How may we help you?'=>'請以英文說明需要我們協助的詳細資訊。','Leave plugin developers any feedback here'=>'請在這裡填寫給外掛開發者的意見反應','Stop export'=>'停止匯出程序','Close'=>'關閉','Please wait, stopping the export...'=>'請稍候，正在停止匯出程序...','Unable to stop the export. Refresh the page and try again'=>'無法停止匯出程序，請重新整理頁面後再試一次。','Unable to run the export. Refresh the page and try again'=>'無法執行匯出程序，請重新整理頁面後再試一次。','Unable to start the export. Refresh the page and try again'=>'無法啟動匯出程序，請重新整理頁面後再試一次。','You are about to stop exporting your website, are you sure?'=>'即將停止匯出網站，確定要繼續操作嗎？','Unable to authenticate the secret key. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-secret-key/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'無法驗證祕密金鑰。<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-secret-key/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a>','Unable to get current pointer position of %s. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/php-32bit/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'無法取得 %s 目前的指標位置。<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/php-32bit/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a>','Unable to seek to offset %d on %s. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/php-32bit/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'無法找到 %d 位移量 (在 %s)。<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/php-32bit/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a>','Unable to read file: %s. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-file-permissions/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'無法讀取檔案 %s。<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-file-permissions/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a>','Out of disk space. Unable to write to: %s. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/out-of-disk-space/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'由於這個網站已無足夠的磁碟空間，因此無法寫入 %s。<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/out-of-disk-space/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a>','Unable to write to: %s. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-file-permissions/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'無法寫入 %s。<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-file-permissions/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a>','Unable to open %s with mode %s. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-file-permissions/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'無法開啟 %s (使用 %s 模式)。<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-file-permissions/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a>','Unable to locate archive path. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-archive-path/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'找不到壓縮檔儲存資料夾路徑。<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-archive-path/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a>','Unable to locate storage path. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-storage-path/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'找不到儲存資料夾路徑。<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-storage-path/" target="_blank">技術詳細資料</a>','I agree that by filling in the contact form with my data, I authorize All-in-One WP Migration to use my <strong>email</strong> to reply to my requests for information. <a href="https://www.iubenda.com/privacy-policy/946881" target="_blank">Privacy policy</a>'=>'在填寫並傳送含有個人資料的聯絡表單後，我同意授權 All-in-One WP Migration 使用我的<strong>電子郵件地址</strong>及相關資訊以回覆我的問題。<a href="https://www.iubenda.com/privacy-policy/946881" target="_blank">隱私權政策</a>','Done preparing configuration file.'=>'組態檔準備已完成。','Preparing configuration file...'=>'正在準備組態檔⋯','Done archiving configuration file.'=>'壓縮組態檔已完成。','Archiving configuration file...<br />%d%% complete'=>'正在壓縮組態檔...<br />已完成 %d%%','2GB+'=>'超過 2GB','Done unpacking archive.'=>'備份檔案解壓縮已完成。','Unpacking archive...<br />%d%% complete'=>'正在解壓縮檔案...<br />已完成 %d%%','Done archiving database.'=>'壓縮資料庫已完成。','Archiving database...<br />%d%% complete'=>'正在壓縮資料庫...<br />已完成 %d%%','Restoring database...<br />%d%% complete'=>'正在還原資料庫...<br />已完成 %d%%','Checking extensions compatibility...'=>'正在檢查擴充功能相容性...','Done restoring database.'=>'還原資料庫已完成。','Preparing to import...'=>'正在準備匯入...','Monthly'=>'每月','Weekly'=>'每週','Do <strong>not</strong> export must-use plugins (files)'=>'<strong>不要</strong>匯出 [強制使用] 外掛 (wp-content/mu-plugins)','Done activating mu-plugins.'=>'啟用 [強制使用] 外掛已完成。','Activating mu-plugins...'=>'正在啟用 [強制使用] 外掛...','Do <strong>not</strong> replace email domain (sql)'=>'<strong>不要</strong>變更電子郵件地址網域名稱 (SQL)','Unrecognized error %s during upload.'=>'上傳檔案時發生無法識別的錯誤 (%s)。','A PHP extension stopped the file upload.'=>'檔案上傳已由 PHP 擴充模組停止。','Failed to write file to disk.'=>'無法將檔案寫入磁碟。','Missing a temporary folder.'=>'找不到暫存資料夾。','Unable to upload the file because %s'=>'無法上傳檔案。原因: %s','Missing tmp_name in upload file.'=>'上傳檔案中缺少 tmp_name。','Missing error key in upload file.'=>'上傳檔案中缺少